{"tid":2463832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何桂藍聽MIRROR新歌爆喊","createTime":"2021-03-27T04:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T11:05:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05b70169a8e6c94308f3813eff9bff12994601fa","tid":2463832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210327/EW5CYEJYWNAG5J6BQZOVUS5TL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210327%2FEW5CYEJYWNAG5J6BQZOVUS5TL4%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=623ac4e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210327%2FEW5CYEJYWNAG5J6BQZOVUS5TL4%2F&h=86225759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210327/EW5CYEJYWNAG5J6BQZOVUS5TL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n何桂藍聽MIRROR新歌爆喊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4H9hXdHAs9ZrtOYAuF3pP_N_JcU=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RVSBIBNESJDTFJ4EW74R4K5TA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4H9hXdHAs9ZrtOYAuF3pP_N_JcU%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRVSBIBNESJDTFJ4EW74R4K5TA4.jpg&h=e30abb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■職工盟幹事勞詠姫（左）和陳昭偉（右）昨探吳敏兒，擔心其腰痛舊患。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】47名民主派因參加初選被控違反國安法的串謀顛覆政權罪，至今只有11人獲保釋。還柙者親友昨繼續探望打氣，職工盟組織幹事勞詠姫到羅湖懲教所探望吳敏兒，勞事後替戰友落淚，「真係好擔心佢，好唔抵」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「大不了死 亦不會避」<br />\n<br />\n職工盟組織幹事陳昭偉昨下午探望吳敏兒後指，吳比還柙前略消瘦但精神不錯，正努力適應，指吳「心理狀態好強大，好佩服」。同行的勞詠姫提及吳更哽咽落淚，「真係好擔心佢，好唔抵，同埋好擔心佢條腰」。陳指，吳的腰痛問題屬舊患，「監獄入面啲床又太硬」，但未有方法解決床鋪問題，「睇吓有冇咩運動可以做吓，幫佢紓緩吓」。<br />\n<br />\n身在大欖女懲教所的何桂藍，其團隊在fb指何收到市民打氣信件，感謝大家關心，亦回信親友與「寫信師」，並交代何「聽到MIRROR嘅新歌Warrior，還柙咁耐以嚟，第一次喊，喊到收唔到聲。 啱呀。大不了死，亦不會避。」網友亦留言鼓勵「撐住，加油，平安」。<br />\n<br />\n前香港眾志組織幹事黃莉莉昨探訪袁嘉蔚後指，袁已轉至大倉，身體精神不錯，並已剪短頭髮，「有啲似小丸子」。袁現閱讀小說和詩集度日。<br />\n<br />\n早前受審時曾入院的元朗區議員王百羽，其健康狀況一直令外界擔憂，王的友人昨到荔枝角收押所探訪後稱，王比以往消瘦，但血壓已回復正常，「唔可以話佢係開懷，但至少唔係愁雲慘霧嘅情況」。"},{"pid":"b1d0c3a7306672afac592c8fe2deba4b50140c6e","tid":2463832,"uid":130079,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"貼呢d咪好囉<br />\n<br />\n下下貼黃世澤d戇鳩評論做咩呢"},{"pid":"6e5328d42924916ff89a206d1c24f20978ec36b0","tid":2463832,"uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"#1 ON TRENDING<br />\n<br />\nMIRROR 《WARRIOR》Official Music Video<br />\nMar 26, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YI4qsJhZtwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYI4qsJhZtwA&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=39abaaca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YI4qsJhZtwA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMIRROR<br />\n72.5K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n昨日的間尺、刻度、單位、標準與貨幣<br />\n量度不了明天的長短、輕重、價值與成敗。<br />\n老海鮮是無法明白新物種的。<br />\n<br />\n未死的不會因為口誅筆伐而氣絕身亡，<br />\n已死的不會因為搖尾乞憐而無限復活，<br />\n糾纏在「XX已死」、「乜乜已死」的爭論是那麼多此一舉，<br />\n只有懷著打不死的戰意信仰精神，即使地球已死，我們還有開拓新宇宙的戰鬥力。<br />\n每人每天都是披著戰士袍打出新版圖。<br />\n <br />\n#MIRROR​ #WARRIOR​<br />\n <br />\n《WARRIOR》<br />\n <br />\n曲：Val Del Prete / Hwan Yang<br />\n詞：林若寧<br />\nRap詞 ：Lokman@MIRROR / Alton@MIRROR<br />\n編：Val Del Prete / Hwan Yang / Edward Chan <br />\n監：Edward Chan<br />\n唱：MIRROR<br />\n<br />\n笨蛋 虛偽 阻擋火車衝不出新路軌<br />\n壞蛋 拉關係 新推出測謊機誰用地位關掣<br />\n高級的 低質的 力量範圍 困住了階梯<br />\n給挑剔 給威迫 未下跪天規靠信仰打低<br />\n <br />\n難成為習慣做一隻棋 行動都顧忌<br />\n挺起腰骨被負評練勇氣 挺起胸襟任未來不似預期<br />\n大不了死 亦不會避<br />\n念力能做武器 滴汗能做武器<br />\n新聲音慘遭攻擊有了準備<br />\n <br />\n浩浩蕩蕩迎來另一新世紀<br />\n越鬧越熱鬧是轉機 越靜默越寂寞難有驚喜<br />\n運用念力凡人亦都可以飛<br />\n拆去幾多關卡 多了幾多怪咖 擁抱他 以新血灌溉天地<br />\n <br />\nRAP<br />\n我捉緊 獨有氣魄 靠節拍 <br />\n吹散困惑 無視踐踏<br />\n專注鑄 造盔甲 出發 攻塔<br />\n將陳舊規格續一續一 續一擊殺<br />\n用汗與血作抵押無懼孤注一擲<br />\n <br />\n新基因 新膚色 後浪面前（別販賣著舊軟件 別賣弄著舊日經典）<br />\n新規則 新東西 做實驗（實驗一支一支一支火箭）<br />\n <br />\n成員未退出讓陰暗面 成敗都正面<br />\n以閃光燈在地球大作戰 以咪高風大預言一個十年<br />\n冒一次險 發一次電 越定型越要變 越技窮越要變<br />\n超光速火星軌跡快過閃電<br />\n <br />\n浩浩蕩蕩迎來另一新世紀<br />\n越鬧越熱鬧是轉機 越靜默越寂寞難有驚喜<br />\n運用念力凡人亦都可以飛<br />\n拆去幾多關卡 多了幾多怪咖 擁抱他 以新血灌溉天地<br />\n <br />\nnever give up never give up<br />\nnever give up I got it I&rsquo;ve got a warrior heart<br />\nnever give up never give up<br />\nnever give up I got it I&rsquo;ve got a warrior heart<br />\n <br />\nRAP<br />\n封閉嘅態度 我畫上句號<br />\n新世界創造 一班被選中嘅細路<br />\n不驕 不傲 不斷變化再進化 引發 連場風暴<br />\n訊號 收到 出發偉大航道<br />\n <br />\n標準有新嘗試 摩打有新電池<br />\n殘舊配件很有事  停頓再開始<br />\n新的古蹟新的史詩不設定義<br />\n輾轉反側即將湧出新一批幼齒<br />\n <br />\n浩浩蕩蕩迎來另一新世紀<br />\n越鬧越熱鬧是轉機 越靜默越寂寞難有驚喜<br />\n聚集念力凡人亦都可以飛<br />\n勇氣只可開機 相信總可以飛 新世紀 我請你要有準備<br />\n <br />\nnever give up never give up<br />\nnever give up I got it I&rsquo;ve got a warrior heart<br />\nnever give up never give up<br />\nnever give up I got it I&rsquo;ve got a warrior heart<br />\n<br />\nOP: Music Jam (admin by Sony Music Publishing Korea Ltd.)/ 1111<br />\nSP: Sony Music Publishing (HK) Ltd/ Warner Chappell Music, Hong Kong Limited<br />\n<br />\nAll Instruments by Val Del Prete / Hwan Yang<br />\nexcept Additional Programming by Edward Chan / Michael Wong <br />\n<br />\nRap Produced by 李一丁/ Edward Chan <br />\nAdditional Vocal Produced by Cousin Fung<br />\n<br />\nBacking Vocals by Soho<br />\nBacking Vocals Edited by Soho / Cousin Fung <br />\n<br />\nProtools Editing by Edward Chan/ Anson Chan/ Kelvin Au/ Cousin Fung/ Soho/ 李一丁<br />\nRecorded by Edward Chan/ Anson Chan/ Cousin Fung/ Soho/ 李一丁/ King Kong@nova<br />\nMixed by Matthew Sim"},{"pid":"25ffc0cc7bfba52be65b3253261968699c3761b9","tid":2463832,"uid":28759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"都真係幾有 feel"},{"pid":"e588a7ea0e274ac1a3ef60b32daef2b3221e64fa","tid":2463832,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"賣完慘情未<br />\n之前又話咩係獄中關注手足<br />\n又一篇新聞<br />\n而家又話邊個邊個喊<br />\n又一篇新聞<br />\n<br />\n九十二籤幫手封關上庭，有無出過報導？<br />\nYOUTUBER告暴動又有得出過？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQq7Cmy2HPBNxPAwfvdL1k5puSgCBy9Lhw6zgK7xbR2Au?filename=KzHdg8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzHdg8F.jpg&h=44d6f07b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTHtNHY4bDWkfQhppkfPAEp2mupcJURFFNLCCGpKsjAFx?filename=yOmmq11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOmmq11.png&h=b2fc6b50&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地緬甸係諗點樣贏<br />\n香港人就係諗點樣歌頌被打壓既人<br />\n賣慘情<br />\n之後同你講乜野抗爭都係無用，等如送頭<br />\n等國際線打救，同埋移民<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQtjkGfoctRiD2QW88ZN59z1ZgtRXPyU5t14iJzLuRBGP?filename=Vi7kxOS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVi7kxOS.jpg&h=2f49d72d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWF4qD3nqdFWf4M44dgRgP4eguNsLKTWtCBTtc6Gn59wB?filename=jkqKe2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkqKe2b.jpg&h=0d2f5701&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWyrE6KcndATWFnDoC3aTqxxuumVo1XsNjdnhPrVNUM5K?filename=OvGaaAt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvGaaAt.jpg&h=52f5a461&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRzJp2B2tnmvge7fZiswjrWFqCd1vaNFY8gDqMYsMPpPt?filename=o0fREtO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0fREtO.jpg&h=4a524159&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWBXWk7QVqU5SZPQZAiee1FFZPeFwqQWjJdaZohGSA1jr?filename=75QqJVx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75QqJVx.jpg&h=eee4ba70&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcJjdkZTndt4ssqHefmifX6viPraPoKb7hYxzk91E1xEu?filename=uWB11Hb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWB11Hb.jpg&h=0a820ab5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSEYVY3cTSiS1akz5Z5Y3fSAJj45yxnwYnXwgCFCdvE5R?filename=GPQeCfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPQeCfw.jpg&h=027c2e85&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNi3k4PSTeuneeAuTwgKkF1hL2UAtE54FfsrE5vpg6Nvs?filename=nhDscOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhDscOR.jpg&h=3e555821&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n</blockquote> <br />\n上面所有抗爭都唔撚好做，係送頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmREMtKQoqvoEMfKMyZg4UPao7jw1b1UPJWshGk29ymCtD?filename=2NWmhfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NWmhfv.jpg&h=0cb8e5db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n灌輸既意識形態係同你講<br />\n所有野都應該放棄，無得鬥，應該移民救港，等國際線打救<br />\n無野可以做，或者下年參加下立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n蘋果呢份報紙想做乜顯然易見<br />\n陣間又點樣爭取到係制度入面一點光，參加選舉為香港人發聲？<br />\n之後又會造啲咩巨聲出黎幫呢班被打壓既手足？<br />\n之後又整個基金出黎<br />\n基金又唔係用黎諗點贏，難聽啲講句，係諗點樣買棺材<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"9d61163c0efb9bbe64c19d7db1148bd0d7f3ed78","tid":2463832,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Rap詞 ：Lokman@MIRROR / Alton@MIRROR<br />\n<br />\nRAP<br />\n封閉嘅態度 我畫上句號<br />\n新世界創造 <span class=\"red\">一班被選中嘅細路</span><br />\n不驕 不傲 不斷變化再進化 引發 連場風暴<br />\n訊號 收到 <span class=\"gold\">出發偉大航道</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">紅字</span> 好地地用TVB卡通做白欖米乖乖仔lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">黃字</span> 竟然敢用ATV卡通兩條白欖友未死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/gbDm9f-EMrA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FgbDm9f-EMrA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=3a311d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">海賊王 ONE PIECE 亞洲電視 ATV 粵語 Cantonese OPENING 主題曲 OP<br />\n5,971 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=d3RCFy2u-UA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h